data.description: Welcome to this impeccable 4-bedroom, 3-bath, 3-car garage oasis nestled in the highly sought-after Polo Run community of Lakewood Ranch. This elegant Tivoli model home is ideally situated just steps away from the vibrant amenities center, making it a perfect haven for families and active individuals alike. Positioned on a serene conservation lot, this single-story gem boasts a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, offering privacy and functionality. With its 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and spacious 3-car garage, you'll enjoy the convenience of modern living in this charming, low-maintenance, gated community. Polo Run takes community living to the next level, offering a plethora of amenities for you and your loved ones to enjoy. Revel in the resort-style heated pool, socialize in the gathering room, work up a sweat in the expansive fitness center, or engage in wellness activities in the yoga and aerobics room. Sports enthusiasts will appreciate the tennis and pickleball courts, as well as the half basketball court. Additionally, there are bocce ball courts, a playground for the little ones, and even a dedicated dog park for your furry friends. Notably, Polo Run is also a solar-powered community, highlighting its commitment to sustainability. Step inside this nearly new home, where you'll find tasteful diagonal neutral tile adorning the main living areas, complemented by elegant crown molding. The brick paver driveway and lanai add to the overall curb appeal. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's dream with its open layout, wraparound counter, center island, and a cozy breakfast nook. It's complete with top-notch stainless steel appliances and stunning granite countertops, making meal preparation a breeze. Retreat to the owner's suite, which boasts a spacious walk-in closet, a luxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, and dual sinks, offering a serene sanctuary for relaxation. One of the three additional bedrooms even has its own private bathroom, perfect for guests or a growing family. Rest easy knowing that this home was built to hurricane code standards and features code-compliant hurricane panels, ensuring your family's safety during stormy weather. Beyond the community's offerings, Lakewood Ranch itself offers a wealth of green spaces, parks, and trails for outdoor enthusiasts. Additionally, a short drive takes you to Main Street, where you can enjoy shopping and dining, or to the University Town Center for even more entertainment options. This home in Polo Run is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle waiting for you to embrace. Don't miss this opportunity to make it yours today.
